---
layout: "baseof.njk"
title: "Vegan Homecooking by Tiff & Laura"
---

<div class="top-container">
  <div class="max-w-screen-md mb-12 mx-auto bg-gray-50 shadow p-8">
    <h1 class="top-header">
      {{ title }}
    </h1>
    <p>
      A pretty website free of ads, long SEO preludes, or weird design choices
      to chronicle some of our favorite original and adapted recipes.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="md:w-2/3 p-4 mb-8">
    <div class="bg-gray-50 shadow p-4">
      <h2 class="top-header text-center">A Few of Our Favorites</h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap">
        {% for item in collections.recipe %}
        <li class="md:w-1/2 md:p-2 h-full relative">
          {% include "recipeList.njk" %}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="md:w-1/3 p-4">
    <div class="bg-gray-50 shadow p-4">
      <h2 class="top-header text-center">All Categories</h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center px-4 text-center text-base">
        {% for tag in collections.tagList %}
        <li
          class="border-2 border-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-800 hover:text-gray-200 m-1"
        >
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}" class="block py-2 px-4">{{ tag }}</a>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="top-header">Notes</h2>
    <div class="markdown">
      <ul>
        <li>Biscuits and Gravy</li>
        <li>Chili</li>
        <li>Enchiladas</li>
        <li>Tacos</li>
        <li>Spicy Potatoes</li>
        <li>Noodles</li>
        <li>Cheesecake</li>
        <li>Chocolate chip cookies</li>
        <li>Marys Tofu chik'n</li>
        <li>Loaded sweet potatoes</li>
        <li>Loaded baked potatoes</li>
        <li>Tempeh bacon</li>
        <li>seitan</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
